---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ & Rules | Ellamin Courtyard Retreat" description="Review common questions and guidelines to maintain a friendly, safe stay environment.">
  <section class="v3-band pb-12">
    <div class="v3-container">
      <div class="mb-7">
        <p class="v3-eyebrow">Trust Registry</p>
        <h2 class="v3-section-title mt-3 font-display">FAQ & House Rules</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[color:var(--muted)] max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Review common questions and guidelines to maintain a friendly, safe stay environment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start mt-10">
        
        <!-- House Rules -->
        <div class="v3-card p-8 flex flex-col gap-6">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--ink)] border-b border-[color:var(--line)] pb-3">House Rules</h3>
          
          <ul class="text-xs text-[color:var(--muted)] flex flex-col gap-4">
            <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-base" aria-hidden="true">🚭</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-[color:var(--ink)]">No Smoking Inside</strong>
                <p class="mt-0.5">Smoking is strictly restricted to designated outdoor balcony or deck areas. A RM 200 fee applies for odors.</p>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li class="flex gap-3 items-start border-t border-[color:var(--line)] pt-4">
              <span class="text-base" aria-hidden="true">🔇</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-[color:var(--ink)]">Quiet Hours (10:00 PM - 8:00 AM)</strong>
                <p class="mt-0.5">Please lower music volumes and vacate outdoor pool decks by 10:00 PM to respect neighbors.</p>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li class="flex gap-3 items-start border-t border-[color:var(--line)] pt-4">
              <span class="text-base" aria-hidden="true">🐾</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-[color:var(--ink)]">No Pets Allowed</strong>
                <p class="mt-0.5">Pets are strictly prohibited inside the rooms or pool areas due to community bylaws.</p>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li class="flex gap-3 items-start border-t border-[color:var(--line)] pt-4">
              <span class="text-base" aria-hidden="true">🏊</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-[color:var(--ink)]">Pool Safety</strong>
                <p class="mt-0.5">No glass bottles or glassware near the pool water. Children must be supervised by adults.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQs -->
        <div class="v3-card p-8 flex flex-col gap-6">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--ink)] border-b border-[color:var(--line)] pb-3">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-xs text-[color:var(--muted)]">
            <div>
              <strong class="text-[color:var(--ink)]">What are the check-in and check-out times?</strong>
              <p class="mt-1">Check-in is from 3:00 PM onwards, and check-out is by 12:00 PM. Early check-in requires package approval.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t border-[color:var(--line)] pt-4">
              <strong class="text-[color:var(--ink)]">How do I access the property?</strong>
              <p class="mt-1">We use a smart-keypad lock. A temporary 4-digit code will be generated and sent via WhatsApp 2 hours before arrival.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t border-[color:var(--line)] pt-4">
              <strong class="text-[color:var(--ink)]">Is Wi-Fi available?</strong>
              <p class="mt-1">Yes, high-speed fiber internet is provided free of charge. Access details are listed on the dining table board.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t border-[color:var(--line)] pt-4">
              <strong class="text-[color:var(--ink)]">Are cooking utensils provided?</strong>
              <p class="mt-1">The kitchen is equipped with induction cooker, microwave, refrigerator, frying pans, and standard plates/bowls.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
